name: Rasim Öztekin
summary: Rasim Öztekin. Actor: G.O.R.A.. Rasim Öztekin was born on 14 January 1959 in Istanbul, Turkey. He was an actor, known for G.O.R.A. (2004), Kabadayi (2007) and Dügün Dernek (2013). He was previously married to Esra Kazancibasi. He died on 8 March 2021 in Istanbul, Turkey.
